---
title: Cheesy Tex-Mex Plant-Based Mince & Avocado Tacos with Slaw & Sweetcorn
description: That’s right it’s taco night, our favourite time of the week has come around and oh boy do we have a taco for you! Pack the
tortillas with fresh avo and creamy plant-based mayo to go with Tex-Mex spiced veggie mince and that’s a wrap on taco night.

